{"tid":1632752,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【不怪任何人】超儀遭超瓊拒絕開騷申請 疑政治立場影響審批","createTime":"2019-10-06T21:17:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T15:57:57.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"17d7670cc1b0acb086f0987627a614e9026493a4","tid":1632752,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T21:17:27.000Z","msg":"何超瓊與胞妹何超儀一向感情不錯，超瓊更相當支持妹妹發展娛樂圈事業，曾從家族基金撥錢給她投資拍片，所以超儀是很尊重這位家姐，但據聞最近兩姊妹為一個演唱會批文鬧分歧。<br />\n<br />\n但超儀與她的樂隊Josie &amp; The Uni Boys，於今年4月聯同中港台搖滾勁旅，包括：LMF、廿四味、秋紅主音Jan、激膚樂團、怕胖團、地獄貓樂團DH及特別嘉賓林子祥等，在香港舉行了「The Classic Purple Psycho Experience」音樂會，由於反應不錯，超儀已經計劃好，將整個騷搬到澳門演出，所以隨即向姐姐超瓊旗下賭場酒店申請檔期，可惜申請數月，仍未有回音。<br />\n<br />\n據知申請不果與政治有關，由於Josie &amp; The Uni Boys的成員擺明是「黃」底，而且LMF早前亦投訴過「撐警集會」在未得他們同意而使用了組合其中一首歌在大會播放，出了嚴正聲明表示不滿；至於隊員之一MC仁，曾為反國教製作「洗腦教育」歌。可是超瓊卻是「撐警」的一方，她在上月才以「香港的真實情況」（On the true situation of Hong Kong, China）為題，去信過聯合國大會，聲稱要反映本港真實的情況，批評激進示威者騎劫《逃犯條例》修訂，並強調一小撮激進分子不代表全港750萬人意見，更稱香港人支持政府停止廣泛暴亂，拘捕暴力示威者；信中又力數示威者有計劃地抹黑警方令公眾仇警。<br />\n<br />\n有指超儀對家姐不撐自己心裏感到不開心，今日超儀回應《蘋果》時表示：「我哋冇嗌交，只不過係屋企飯局閒聊，家姐婉拒咗我，話呢類騷唔適合佢啲客聽喎！唔緊要，我哋係一家人，所以會了解到外來不可抗力嘅壓迫，所以我唔會怪任何一位人。東家唔打咪打西家囉！暫時咪唔搞呢啲演唱會住，荷李活有啲阿四角色畀我做，咁我咪做住先啦！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191006/large/1570363221_03a2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191006%2Flarge%2F1570363221_03a2.jpg&h=227b73a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191006/60124559\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191006%2F60124559&d=QZYHYFPECKJw76TN47EEpvMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=0d3ff9e9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191006%2F60124559&h=433689fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191006/60124559</a>"},{"pid":"5b4465216ef11b2ab0b29d0aab2f86971ec5e7fd","tid":1632752,"uid":50196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T21:38:52.000Z","msg":"何超係藍定黃？"},{"pid":"e240a739f94349d52b6f001209a365009cd249e2","tid":1632752,"uid":152123,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"5b4465216ef11b2ab0b29d0aab2f86971ec5e7fd","tid":1632752,"uid":50196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T21:38:52.000Z","msg":"何超係藍定黃？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T21:44:54.000Z","msg":"梗係黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ea09c38ead455e93d4939952ecfdd64919d590b","tid":1632752,"uid":137604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:00:08.000Z","msg":"關澳門當局事多D<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcce55563be5ca88fa8ffa077310c6ddc46c282c","tid":1632752,"uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9ea09c38ead455e93d4939952ecfdd64919d590b","tid":1632752,"uid":137604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:00:08.000Z","msg":"關澳門當局事多D<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:49:19.000Z","msg":"我覺得兩樣都有"},{"pid":"da6a96adcaf8948a83641dd683e656cf1fe440f2","tid":1632752,"uid":55519,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"e240a739f94349d52b6f001209a365009cd249e2","tid":1632752,"uid":152123,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"5b4465216ef11b2ab0b29d0aab2f86971ec5e7fd","tid":1632752,"uid":50196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T21:38:52.000Z","msg":"何超係藍定黃？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T21:44:54.000Z","msg":"梗係黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:28:22.000Z","msg":"我覺得佢係冇乜立場"},{"pid":"c8bb61a35558eea8c315b02c1c5889f9012a9919","tid":1632752,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da6a96adcaf8948a83641dd683e656cf1fe440f2","tid":1632752,"uid":55519,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"e240a739f94349d52b6f001209a365009cd249e2","tid":1632752,"uid":152123,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"5b4465216ef11b2ab0b29d0aab2f86971ec5e7fd","tid":1632752,"uid":50196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T21:38:52.000Z","msg":"何超係藍定黃？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T21:44:54.000Z","msg":"梗係黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:28:22.000Z","msg":"我覺得佢係冇乜立場"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T15:57:57.000Z","msg":"Juno咁<br />\n<br />\n藝術到唔需要有立場<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n未必係黃<br />\n<br />\n但唔會因為黃而封殺人"}]}